@@ -1054,6 +1054,25 @@ /** * The {@code abstract} keyword. * + *

For example:

+ * 
+     *  public abstract class MyClass
+     *  {
+     *  }
+     *
+ *

parses as:

+ * 
+     * --CLASS_DEF
+     *    |--MODIFIERS
+     *    |   |--LITERAL_PUBLIC (public)
+     *    |   `--ABSTRACT (abstract)
+     *    |--LITERAL_CLASS (class)
+     *    |--IDENT (MyClass)
+     *    `--OBJBLOCK
+     *        |--LCURLY ({)
+     *        `--RCURLY (})
+     *
+ * * @see #MODIFIERS **/ public static final int ABSTRACT = GeneratedJavaTokenTypes.ABSTRACT;
